# Plan 6: Admin Panel - Music Management

## Goal
Build the admin interface to upload and manage tracks.

## Tasks
- [ ] Create `app/admin/music/page.tsx`.
- [ ] Implement a file upload component using `react-dropzone` for audio and artwork.
- [ ] Create a Server Action `uploadTrack` to save files to `/public/uploads` and insert records into the DB.
- [ ] (Optional) Generate waveform data on the server during upload (using a node library or client-side pre-processing).
- [ ] Create a data table to list existing tracks with edit/delete options.
- [ ] Add form fields for metadata: Title, Artist, Album, Genre, BPM.
